<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.logging.LogManager.SetIncludeSeverity" Title="SetIncludeSeverity method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.LogManager">LogManager</PageRef> ->
    SetIncludeSeverity
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>SetIncludeSeverity</TypeRef> method sets the manager-level severity filter. Messages that do not pass this filter are discarded before any target-specific filter is evaluated.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
      This method is safe to call concurrently with logging and target registration.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void SetIncludeSeverity(ILogger::SeverityFilter value);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="SeverityFilter!cobalt.logging.ILogger.SeverityFilter" Name="value">The new manager-level severity filter.</ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="See also">
